<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Our Story | Honourable Ladies of Value Foundation</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>

.header-section {
    position: relative;
    background-image: url('/images/about.jpg'); /* Replace with your header image */
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    color: white;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    padding: 100px 0;
    text-align: center;
}

/* Overlay style */
.header-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.621);  /* Dark overlay, adjust opacity for desired thickness */
    z-index: 1;  /* Ensure overlay is above the background but below the text */
}

.header-section h1, .header-section p {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;  /* Ensure text is above the overlay */
}


        .heading-primary {
            color: #1b479e; /* Navy Blue */
        }

        .highlight {
            color: #fb8127; /* Pink */
        }

/* Section Background */
.section-bg {
    background-color: #f4f4f4; /* Light background color for the section */
}

/* Curved Image Style */
.rounded-image {
    border-radius: 15px;  /* Adjust this to control the curvature of the image */
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Optional: adds shadow to the image */
}

/* Image Container with Design */
.image-container {
    position: relative;
}

/* Background Design on Left Column */
.background-design {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 50%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #fb8127; /* Pink background color */
    border-radius: 15px 0 0 15px;  /* Matches the image's curvature */
    z-index: -1; /* Pushes the design behind the image */
}

/* Blockquote Styling */
.blockquote {
    font-style: italic;
    border-left: 4px solid #1b479e; /* Navy blue border */
    padding-left: 20px;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #333;
}

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../../partials/header') %>
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <header class="header-section">
        <h1 class="display-4">Our Story</h1>
        <p class="lead">Empowering widows, orphans, and the underprivileged through love, support, and opportunity.</p>
    </header>

    <!-- The Beginning Section -->
    <section class="py-5 section-bg">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h2 class="heading-primary">The Beginning</h2>
                    <p>Our journey began with a shared vision to create lasting change, one life at a time. We recognized the challenges facing widows and orphans in Nigeria and sought to provide practical solutions to alleviate their suffering. What started as a small initiative has blossomed into a movement of compassion, impact, and hope.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <img style="border-radius: 20px;" src="/images/start.png" class="img-fluid" alt="The Beginning">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Impact Section -->
    <section class="py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="heading-primary text-center">Our Impact So Far</h2>
            <p class="text-center">Since our inception, we have made significant strides in empowering women, children, and families in need.</p>
            
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card shadow-sm">
                        <img src="/images/Empower.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Business Empowerment">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Empowering Women</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">We have helped countless women rebuild or start their businesses, providing the resources and training needed to succeed.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card shadow-sm">
                        <img src="/images/orphans.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Education for Orphans">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Education for Orphans</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">We provide quality educational opportunities to orphaned children, giving them the tools to build a better future.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card shadow-sm">
                        <img src="/images/honourable30.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Healthcare Access">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Healthcare Access</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">We ensure families in need have access to vital healthcare, addressing their most urgent medical requirements.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

<!-- Founder’s Message Section -->
<section class="py-5 section-bg">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <!-- Left Column with Design and Curved Image -->
            <div class="col-md-6 position-relative">
                <div class="image-container">
                    <img src="/images/leaders.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded-image" alt="Theresa Oby Ogoegbunam">
                </div>
                <div class="background-design"></div> <!-- Design on the left side -->
            </div>
            <!-- Right Column with Text -->
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2 class="heading-primary text-center mb-4">Founder’s Message</h2>

                <p class="blockquote text-center">"Our mission is to empower the marginalized and uplift those who have been forgotten by society. Through education, support, and healthcare, we help them reclaim their dignity and future."</p>
                <p class="text-center"><strong>Theresa Oby Ogoegbunam, Founder & CEO</strong></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<%- include('../../partials/testimonies') %>


    <!-- Footer Partial (Include this in your layout.ejs) -->
    <%- include('../../partials/footer') %>

